caption: This tribal music is played on a didgeridoo. It is played by vibrating the lips over the instrument using breathing techniques. The song has a continuous droning sound and inter spread with low pitch bass sounds. There are no voices in this song. This audio can be used in a movie where the protagonist is trapped in a forest.
